title: New Sioux Falls Restaurant Plans To Open This Week
text:
New Sioux Falls Restaurant Plans To Open This Week October 19, 2015, 4:47 PM SIOUX FALLS, SD - 
Moe's Southwest Grill is getting ready to open its doors in Sioux Falls. 
The Atlanta-based, fast-casual franchise officially opens Thursday morning with the first 75 customers receiving free Moe's burritos once a week for an entire year. 
On Wednesday, Moe's will host a special college and community VIP Party, followed by a fundraising dinner for Roosevelt High School.
